Japheth ([http://sources.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bible%2C_English%2C_King_James%2C_Genesis#Chapter_10 Genesis 10]:2); possibly related to [[יין|יַיִן]] (yayin) "wine" or Greek [[Ἴων]] (Iōn) "Ionian".

